	"description": "[Hold Secondary] Devolve into a spore.\n \n[Secondary + Shift] Reset your devolve progress.\n \nWild Magic Surge:\n \n[Secondary]: If you are holding a netherite hoe, you cause a Wild Magic Surge to spawn, which will cast a random spell every two seconds in a 10 block radius. If this effect is positive, it will affect myconoids. If this effect is negative, it will affect everything else. Costs 20 spores.\n \nThe position of the Wild Magic Surge is telegraphed by particles. It has no armor value, 20 hp and lasts for 15 seconds or until it is destroyed by an enemy, whichever happens first."
